## Import Census Data

Data downloaded from the Census website at https://data.census.gov/cedsci/table?q=Housing%20Units%20in%20the%20United%20States&t=Housing%3AHousing%20Units%3APopulations%20and%20People%3ARace%20and%20Ethnicity&g=0400000US06.050000&y=2019&tid=ACSDP1Y2019.DP05&hidePreview=true

```{r import_data}
data <- read.csv(here("data/census-demographics", "ACSDP1Y2019.DP05_data_with_overlays_2020-09-26T140825.csv"), header = TRUE)
```

```{r review_data}
dim(data)
colnames(data)
str(data)
View(data)
```
